text: Joyce Mvula (born 15 April 1994) is a Malawian netball player. She was selected to represent the Malawi netball team at the 2019 Netball World Cup. She plays in the Netball Superleague with the Manchester Thunder. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Malawian netball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:2019 Netball World Cup players Category:Netball Superleague players Category:Manchester Thunder players Category:Malawian expatriate sportspeople in England
